This software requires Python 2.6+ to run.

pre-requsite 3rd party:

	pip install sqlitedict
	#pip install blessings
	pip install xmodem
	pip install sauce
	pip install requests
        pip install py-bcrypt
        pip install pyftpdlib

Getting Started
================

To start the system, execute command 

	python2.6 engine.py 

Telnet to the port described in default.ini

PuTTy as a client, windows
==========================

From http://nethack.wikia.com/wiki/ibmgraphics,

  On the PuTTY Configuration window (this appears when you first start PuTTY),
select "Translation" under the "Window" configuration in the pane on the left.
Then, in the pulldown menu marked "Received data assumed to be in which
character set", select "cp437". You can then log in to the server as usual.
You may also change this setting and then 'save' the session. The characater
set (as well as other display settings, e.g., the color blue) will be used in
your session from the on.

SyncTerm as a client,
=====================

http://syncterm.bbsdev.net/

xterm, urxvt, uxterm
====================
  (cat<<EOF
xterm*termName: xterm-color
xterm*reverseVideo:     false
xterm*boldMode:         false
xterm*eightBitInput:    true
xterm*metaSendsEscape:  true
xterm*scrollBar:        false
xterm*renderFont:       false
!menu attributes,
xterm*fontMenu.Label: VT Fonts for cp437 and iso-8859-1
xterm*fontMenu*menuLabel.font: -ibm-courier-medium-r-*-*-17-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
xterm*fontMenu*font: -ibm-courier-medium-r-*-*-17-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
xterm*fontMenu.menuLabel.foreground: cyan
!  Default'
xterm*font: -dosemu-vga-*-*-*-*-17-*-*-*-p-*-ibm-cp437
xterm*fontMenu*fontdefault*Label: 17px ibm-cp437 (dosemu)
!  Unreadable'
xterm*font1: -xos4-terminus-*-*-*-*-12-*-*-*-c-*-ibm-cp437
xterm*fontMenu*font1*Label: 12px ibm-cp437 (terminus)
!  Tiny'
xterm*font2: -schumacher-clean-medium-*-*-*-12-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
xterm*fontMenu*font2*Label: 12px iso-8859-1 (schumacher)
!  Small'
xterm*font3: -xos4-terminus-*-*-*-*-14-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
xterm*fontMenu*font3*Label: 14px iso-8859-1 (terminus)
!alternative #1 (+)
!xterm*font3: -misc-fixed-medium-r-*-*-15-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
!xterm*fontMenu*font3*Label: 15px iso-8859-1 (fixed)
!  Medium'
xterm*font4: -ibm-courier-medium-r-*-*-17-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
xterm*fontMenu*font4*Label: 17px iso-8859-1 (fixed)
!alternative #1 (+)
!xterm.vt100.font4: -xos4-terminus-*-*-*-*-24-*-*-*-*-*-iso8859-1
!xterm*fontMenu*font4*Label: 24px iso-8859-1 (terminus)
!  Large'
xterm*font5: -dosemu-vga-*-*-*-*-17-*-*-*-p-*-ibm-cp437
xterm*fontMenu*font5*Label: 17px ibm cp437 (dosemu)
!alternative #1 (+)
!xterm.vt100.font5: -xos4-terminus-*-*-*-*-20-*-*-*-c-*-ibm-cp437
!xterm*fontMenu*font5*Label: 20px ibm cp437 (terminus)
!alternative #3
!xterm*font5: -xos4-terminus-*-*-*-*-16-*-*-*-c-*-ibm-cp437
!xterm*fontMenu*font5*Label: 16px ibm cp437 (terminus)
!  Huge'
xterm*font6: -dosemu-vga-*-*-*-*-*-24-*-*-*-c-*-ibm-cp437
xterm*fontMenu*font6*Label: 24px ibm cp437 (dosemu)
!alternative #1 (+)
!xterm*font6: -dosemu-vga-*-*-*-*-*-19-*-*-*-c-*-ibm-cp437
!xterm*fontMenu*font6*Label: 19px ibm cp437 (dosemu)
xterm*foreground: rgb:a8/a8/a8
xterm*background: rgb:00/00/00
xterm*color0: rgb:00/00/00
xterm*color1: rgb:a8/00/00
xterm*color2: rgb:00/a8/00
xterm*color3: rgb:a8/54/00
xterm*color4: rgb:00/00/a8
xterm*color5: rgb:a8/00/a8
xterm*color6: rgb:00/a8/a8
xterm*color7: rgb:a8/a8/a8
xterm*color8: rgb:54/54/54
xterm*color9: rgb:fc/54/54
xterm*color10: rgb:54/fc/54
